{"tid":917484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［家家有本難唸的經］有冇人好想自己既某一個家人快啲死","createTime":"2018-11-26T12:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T14:47:52.000Z","uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48099ca3e47e6c58c20da95a569cfc3f7bd2f9a4","tid":917484,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"我好撚想我老母早死早著<br />\n<br />\n我細個會諗我咁樣係咪好不孝<br />\n但我依加一啲都唔會咁諗，仲想佢死左就湯雞還神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先唔講由細到大都日日家暴、大吵大鬧，搞到家無寧日<br />\n打人不特止 我地大喇 識反抗佢喇就走去報埋警<br />\n警察嚟到 一係扮可憐 一係兇番人地轉頭<br />\n前者就當場調停，後者就比俾人塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己打人 自己報警 仲要俾人拉埋 要搵返我地比錢佢保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報警多到啲警察認得我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打我地唔緊要 後生仔女仲挨得<br />\n但可憐左我老豆 由細到大我地俾老母打 <br />\n佢都第一時間走出嚟護住我地<br />\n<br />\n但老豆開始老啦 係做開地盤既<br />\n煙酒妓賭毒都唔掂 係個清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個仆街就日日對佢打打罵罵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆係好+唔打女人 所以日日俾個八婆食住上<br />\n有時我同呀哥會幫佢出一啖氣 鬧番佢轉頭 <br />\n但我喜靜既老豆 就會鬧番我地轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排出去街市賣野仲要俾其他檔主圍住告<br />\n要賠30萬 仲要兇老豆幫佢比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食屎啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩件事不了了之 但個on9 仲想告番人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食屎食懵左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近 個八婆好似好急咁趕住離婚<br />\n仲要分層樓比佢 想趕走埋老豆 老豆梗係唔肯 <br />\n話晒當初老豆出8成錢買<br />\n唔講啲十幾廿年佢對我地幾衰<br />\n仲要出去抅佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲想要贍養費！？<br />\n屎都冇得你食呀 冚家ling <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好後悔點解當初有得告佢虐兒既時候 心軟冇告到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n整唔走條死八婆<br />\n<br />\n你幾撚時死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法可以趕走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd47bf8d615835cc4a368998b7eaa9213d81ff1","tid":917484,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"有冇人入嚟圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff39fa85ba8387c1da5a16953619bde2855c4b9b","tid":917484,"uid":220212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"親生老母？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfc665096d1e36a7a962c4433b2edd264ebe5bb","tid":917484,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"你老母有無玩wechat?<br />\n<br />\n扮鬼佬溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15991613dbaa2c8df371751c60011fc8c7af051e","tid":917484,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff39fa85ba8387c1da5a16953619bde2855c4b9b","tid":917484,"uid":220212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"親生老母？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"85696b9d4be61d5e0bb8cfee22a0efbad241cf21","tid":917484,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfc665096d1e36a7a962c4433b2edd264ebe5bb","tid":917484,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"你老母有無玩wechat?<br />\n<br />\n扮鬼佬溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"屌 佢玩fb 日日上去溝鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}